data.description: Rare 4 bedroom THREE FULL bath Condo in the Villas! Fresh paint, new carpet, super clean and ready for it's new owner! Downstairs has a generous size living room with a separate dining kitchen space, a bedroom and a full bath! Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom bathroom with garden tub and walk in closet.  Two additional bedrooms and one more bathroom round out this lovely 4 bedroom home.  All appliances stay!
